# Exclude the broad scripts directory (Next.js / inspect / dev
# tooling that the runtime images don't need) but re-include the
# Cloud Run extension-check CLI subdirectory. Dockerfile.check-extensions
# COPYs from `scripts/check-extensions/` explicitly; without the
# !-exception, the COPY fails with "file not found in build
# context" because Docker excludes the whole `scripts/` directory
# before the COPY runs.
#
# Note: Dockerfile.migrate has the same shape (COPYs `scripts/migrate/`)
# but is not yet deployed — when its first deploy runs, the same
# !-exception will need adding for that subdirectory. Left as a
# follow-up rather than silently expanded here so the change scope
# stays tied to Plan 2 Task 2.
scripts
!scripts/check-extensions
